invalid type: string "External API Rate Limiting Thresholds\r\nThe public gateway enforces a tier-based rate limit. Anonymous users are limited \r\nto 60 requests per minute per IP. Tier 1 authenticated users get 10,000 requests \r\nper hour. If a client breaches these thresholds, the gateway returns an HTTP 429 \r\nToo Many Requests along with a `Retry-After` header.", expected i64ooleanĸĸĸĸĸĸĸĸĸ